                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><date>Monday</date> Morning</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <date>Jany 23/60</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I think it<lb/> due to myself as well as your-<lb/>self that I\n                should give you<lb/> an extract of a letter I re-<lb/>ceived last\n                        <date><sic>friday</sic></date> from <persName>Dr Mayer</persName><lb/> “upon\n                expressing my astonish-<lb/>ment to <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> that you a<lb/>\n                staunch orthodox should<lb/> have applied for a situation<lb/> as minister to a\n                reformed<lb/> congregation he at once and<lb/> very curtly observed He'll do<lb/>\n                anything for money. It was in<lb/> that conversation he told me that<lb/> a Hebrew\n                lady of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> upon<lb/> one occasion of his calling\n                just<lb/> when you left her house, had<lb/> requested him to tell you that<lb/> she\n                wished to dispense with<lb/> your visits for the reason</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3p26qp95/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
