                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>as assigned by <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> be-<lb/>cause you called too often<lb/>\n                and protracted your visits too<lb/> long. He also told me then that<lb/>\n                <persName>Dr Fischel</persName> had related to him the<lb/> fact of your intended\n                conversion.<lb/> The tone of <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> during<lb/> the whole\n                conversation was that<lb/> of indignation and contempt<lb/> produced as then was and\n                is<lb/> still my impression. I say this<lb/> injustice to him, by his belief,\n                that<lb/> you had deceived him with<lb/> regard to your profession of<lb/>\n                orthodoxy.”</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">I am</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">Your obedient servant</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Abraham Harris</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <placeName>Charleston S.C.</placeName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
